{"tid":1603310,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢個陣有個呀叔同我講","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:24:42.000Z","uid":254802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d285625f7936a63bcd5c33fbb3e9355c666a526","tid":1603310,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"佢話我地抗爭出黎要Play smart <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個建議想話比我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要做到成效最大化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話啲工業用嘅潤滑劑好鬼跣<br />\n如果用玻璃樽裝住又唔覺意成樽跌落地下既話<br />\n咁撻地好跣 如果咁穚比狗追你九條街<br />\n當佢地一踩就跣到仆街  呀叔仲講得好開心 <br />\n向後仆會比玻璃整到屎忽<br />\n向前仆就比玻璃大大力錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你哋就有時間走同埋佢地肯定好難追上你地<br />\n最重要呢樣絕對唔觸犯法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n**********<br />\n<br />\n最後有小小感想<br />\n我知道大家出到黎好驚 我都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地諗下其實前線手足會比你更加驚<br />\n所以唔好一叫你退後就跑到無影<br />\n比班狗見到我地咁一定笑鳩我地<br />\n希望大家可以突破心理障礙<br />\n因為我地行出黎係話比人聽我吔<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔會怕呢個暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n10.1 賀你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"93b1a91683c5e1d2cd9b7d8688d80bde58987e0d","tid":1603310,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"一齊賀佢老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhwF7kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhwF7kd.jpg&h=5781479b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v40Ly0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv40Ly0d.jpg&h=3864b67f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原po在此：<br />\n【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a></span>"},{"pid":"c4d0de05af20ded832d43648d60adc6bb18606fc","tid":1603310,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfb34623f44ae503c2ceee05cf2b80e7d118a9d","tid":1603310,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7d61946240ffb322ce652976999e589640a07f","tid":1603310,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d285625f7936a63bcd5c33fbb3e9355c666a526","tid":1603310,"uid":254802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"佢話我地抗爭出黎要Play smart <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個建議想話比我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要做到成效最大化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話啲工業用嘅潤滑劑好鬼跣<br />\n如果用玻璃樽裝住又唔覺意成樽跌落地下既話<br />\n咁撻地好跣 如果咁穚比狗追你九條街<br />\n當佢地一踩就跣到仆街  呀叔仲講得好開心 <br />\n向後仆會比玻璃整到屎忽<br />\n向前仆就比玻璃大大力錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你哋就有時間走同埋佢地肯定好難追上你地<br />\n最重要呢樣絕對唔觸犯法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n**********<br />\n<br />\n最後有小小感想<br />\n我知道大家出到黎好驚 我都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地諗下其實前線手足會比你更加驚<br />\n所以唔好一叫你退後就跑到無影<br />\n比班狗見到我地咁一定笑鳩我地<br />\n希望大家可以突破心理障礙<